These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, fantasy, horror, satire, scientific, superhero
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: blues, classical, jazz, r&b, reggae, rock, soul
House: gothic-revival, futuristic, townhouse, ranch-style, farmhouse, craftsman, modern
 1. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
 2. the futuristic house is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 3. the modern house is between the fan of classical and the fan of blues##2
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is the modern house##1
 7. the fan of r&b is between the ranch-style house and the person watching satire movies##2
 8. the farmhouse house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 9. the craftsman house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
10. the person watching superhero movies is the fan of jazz##1
11. the fan of rock is the person watching horror movies##1
12. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
13. the gothic-revival house is the fan of reggae##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is between the townhouse house and the modern house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | comedy     | scientific | disaster | horror | superhero  | fantasy  |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | r&b        | classical  | soul     | rock   | jazz       | reggae   |
| House         | futuristic   | modern | ranch-style    | townhouse  | farmhouse | craftsman | gothic-revival |

