 9. the townhouse house is on the far right##1
10. the engineer is on the right of the musician##1
11. the gothic-revival house is the accountant##1
12. the engineer is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the journalist##1
14. the townhouse house is the person drinking water##1
15. the victorian house is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
