 2. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 5. the person playing backgammon is the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the owner of the cat is between the person playing monopoly and the person playing canasta##2
 7. the person playing domino is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking water is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 9. the owner of the pony is the person drinking coffee##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person playing poker is the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the person playing poker is the owner of the hedgehog##1
13. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person playing domino##1
14. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
15. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |   4    |      5      |       6        |       7       |
