The people prefer 7 different types of sport: soccer, handball, volleyball, badminton, baseball, cricket, rowing
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, quad-bike, scooter, ship, snowmobile, taxi, trike
 1. the person driving the trike is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is baking##2
 2. the person driving the trike is the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is the person driving the snowmobile##1
10. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's sport is baseball##1
13. the person driving the ship is the person who's sport is cricket##1
14. the person who's hobby is baking is the person driving the boat##1
15. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1

