 2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is in the middle##1
 7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
