 9. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching romance movies and the person who's sport is rowing##2
10. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
11. the person watching crime movies is the person traveling to venice##1
12. the person watching spy movies is in the middle##1
13. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
